126
00:03:58.300 --> 00:04:01.930
Excuse me, but... please let me through.

127
00:04:03.810 --> 00:04:06.100
Even if you ask nicely...

128
00:04:06.100 --> 00:04:08.640
"no" means...

129
00:04:08.640 --> 00:04:10.150
no!

130
00:04:14.030 --> 00:04:14.820
Okay.

131
00:04:15.190 --> 00:04:16.110
Then...

132
00:04:16.490 --> 00:04:17.820
brace yourselves!

133
00:04:18.150 --> 00:04:19.490
Cocky pirate!

134
00:04:19.490 --> 00:04:21.280
Gum-Gum...

135
00:04:23.240 --> 00:04:24.620
Ally Robot!

136
00:04:32.790 --> 00:04:34.800
Hey! That's dirty!

137
00:04:34.800 --> 00:04:36.380
We can't hit him now!

138
00:04:38.800 --> 00:04:40.800
What a childish trick!

139
00:04:40.800 --> 00:04:42.510
Don't hold back!

140
00:04:43.930 --> 00:04:45.350
Ally Robot...

141
00:04:45.350 --> 00:04:47.520
Punch!

142
00:04:48.310 --> 00:04:49.020
Sorry!

143
00:04:51.190 --> 00:04:53.060
Ally Robot Kick!

144
00:04:55.440 --> 00:04:57.740
I'm so sorry, sir!

145
00:04:57.740 --> 00:04:59.650
That's enough!

146
00:05:00.490 --> 00:05:02.620
Your back is wide open!

147
00:05:13.580 --> 00:05:14.460
You bastard!

148
00:05:24.470 --> 00:05:25.600
Bring him down!

149
00:05:25.600 --> 00:05:27.810
It's just one unarmed man!

150
00:05:50.580 --> 00:05:53.040
How in the world is he so agile?!

151
00:05:53.040 --> 00:05:55.040
I'm in a hurry.

152
00:05:55.420 --> 00:05:57.130
More people are coming later!

153
00:05:57.130 --> 00:05:58.380
See ya!

154
00:06:01.920 --> 00:06:03.510
Huh?!

155
00:06:05.390 --> 00:06:08.350
Hey... stop!

156
00:06:08.890 --> 00:06:11.770
He got through! Hurry! Get inside!

157
00:06:11.770 --> 00:06:13.900
He's on the main island!

158
00:06:13.900 --> 00:06:15.980
Chief, this is the island gate reporting!

159
00:06:15.980 --> 00:06:19.940
S-Straw Hat Luffy has
set foot on the main island!

160
00:06:19.940 --> 00:06:23.360
What?! You let him onto the main island?!

161
00:06:23.360 --> 00:06:25.320
What the hell is going on?!

162
00:06:25.320 --> 00:06:27.120
What are Oimo and Kashi doing?!

163
00:06:27.120 --> 00:06:29.370
Did he take them out too?!

164
00:06:29.740 --> 00:06:33.120
No, sir! It's the middle
of the night right now, so...

165
00:06:34.120 --> 00:06:35.830
they're probably asleep.

166
00:06:35.830 --> 00:06:37.420
This is no time to be sleeping!

167
00:06:37.420 --> 00:06:39.050
Go wake them up!

168
00:06:39.050 --> 00:06:41.710
Wake all the guards on the main island too!

169
00:06:41.710 --> 00:06:43.340
R-Roger!

170
00:06:44.720 --> 00:06:47.140
It's just an intruder.

171
00:06:47.140 --> 00:06:50.510
That's no reason to make
such a fuss, right, Chief?

172
00:06:51.770 --> 00:06:53.980
You've got us.

173
00:06:53.980 --> 00:06:55.600
Don't be ridiculous!

174
00:06:55.600 --> 00:07:01.030
This is the Judicial Island, the sacred,
symbolic entrance into the World Government.

175
00:07:01.650 --> 00:07:07.660
Any idiot should know
what it means to invade this place!

176
00:07:07.660 --> 00:07:13.500
And yet, he broke through to the main island
just to take back a single crew member!

177
00:07:13.500 --> 00:07:16.330
It's an embarrassment!
Who does he think we are?!

178
00:07:17.000 --> 00:07:20.380
Damn those Straw Hats and their accomplices!

179
00:07:20.750 --> 00:07:22.090
Gatekeeper!

180
00:07:22.090 --> 00:07:25.050
Explain what's going on at the main gate!

181
00:07:25.050 --> 00:07:26.340
Hey, gatekeeper!

182
00:07:27.590 --> 00:07:29.220
How many enemies are there?

183
00:07:30.100 --> 00:07:31.640
Where are they?

184
00:07:32.310 --> 00:07:34.680
Come in, main gate!

185
00:07:34.680 --> 00:07:36.440
Hey, what's the matter?!

186
00:07:38.060 --> 00:07:41.270
Come in, gatekeeper!

187
00:07:42.980 --> 00:07:44.650
Rope Action...

188
00:07:44.650 --> 00:07:47.610
Figure-of-Eight Knot!

189
00:07:48.530 --> 00:07:51.280
Bazooka Bat!

190
00:07:53.540 --> 00:07:55.830
Shouldn't waste our ammo just yet!

191
00:07:56.160 --> 00:07:58.750
Get in through the side doors! Open the gate!

192
00:08:03.000 --> 00:08:04.630
Don't let them open it!

193
00:08:05.340 --> 00:08:07.090
– Move it or lose it!
– Move it or lose it!

194
00:08:07.470 --> 00:08:08.840
Mozu! Take the left side!

195
00:08:08.840 --> 00:08:10.640
I'm on it!

196
00:08:11.260 --> 00:08:13.010
Like I'd let you!

197
00:08:13.850 --> 00:08:15.890
Whoa! Hair just popped out of my nose!

198
00:08:16.390 --> 00:08:17.850
You should pay attention!

199
00:08:21.520 --> 00:08:22.310
Get going!

200
00:08:22.310 --> 00:08:24.030
Thanks a bunch!

201
00:08:30.610 --> 00:08:32.950
Keel Breaker!

202
00:08:40.000 --> 00:08:43.710
Are the gates unlocked yet?!
Mozu?! Kiwi?!

203
00:08:44.840 --> 00:08:48.470
Ship demolition is the Franky Family's job.
So picking locks is...

204
00:08:50.760 --> 00:08:52.180
Unlocked on this side!

205
00:08:52.680 --> 00:08:53.890
This side too!

206
00:08:53.890 --> 00:08:59.140
Okay then! Open the gate, Mighty Destroyers!

207
00:09:05.860 --> 00:09:08.650
Don't let them open it! Defend it at all costs!

208
00:09:08.990 --> 00:09:10.240
Move! You're in our way!

209
00:09:25.840 --> 00:09:27.590
Hurry through!

210
00:09:32.430 --> 00:09:35.300
We broke through the first gate!

211
00:09:37.930 --> 00:09:41.440
Whoa! What the hell is with this gaping hole?!

212
00:09:41.440 --> 00:09:43.690
There's no time for sightseeing!

213
00:09:43.690 --> 00:09:45.940
Keep moving!

214
00:09:45.940 --> 00:09:49.110
Stay the course and get to the island gate!

215
00:09:49.110 --> 00:09:51.240
It's a waterfall!

216
00:09:54.740 --> 00:09:55.910
– We did it!
– We did it!

217
00:09:55.910 --> 00:09:58.240
Hey, guys! Over here!

218
00:09:58.240 --> 00:10:00.330
Gimme a hand with this!

219
00:10:07.800 --> 00:10:11.920
Kashi! Oimo! Wake up this instant!

220
00:10:11.920 --> 00:10:16.180
Th-The main gate has been
forced open by intruders!

221
00:10:18.930 --> 00:10:23.730
He said the main gate was forced open, Oimo.

222
00:10:23.730 --> 00:10:25.270
Yeah.

223
00:10:25.270 --> 00:10:29.110
That's not good, Kashi.

224
00:10:32.610 --> 00:10:34.740
I don't wanna get up...

225
00:10:34.740 --> 00:10:36.820
...but it's our job. Let's go do this.

226
00:10:38.620 --> 00:10:40.700
– Alright!
– Alright!

227
00:10:46.540 --> 00:10:49.130
– What?!
– What?!

228
00:10:56.050 --> 00:11:05.980
Oimo
Gatekeeper of
Enies Lobby's Island Gate
Kashi
Gatekeeper of
Enies Lobby's Island Gate

229
00:10:58.300 --> 00:11:00.890
I didn't get enough sleep.

230
00:11:01.720 --> 00:11:04.850
I'll get rid of them quick and go back to bed.

231
00:11:04.850 --> 00:11:05.980
Oimo too.

232
00:11:05.980 --> 00:11:08.650
G-G-Giants!

233
00:11:09.020 --> 00:11:13.610
Dunno why you guys came all the way here,

234
00:11:13.610 --> 00:11:16.740
but I suggest you turn tail
before we crush you.

235
00:11:16.740 --> 00:11:17.740
Right, Oimo?

236
00:11:17.740 --> 00:11:20.580
Yeah, Kashi. Oimo agrees.

237
00:11:21.290 --> 00:11:24.710
We'll crush you flat, bones and all!

238
00:11:24.710 --> 00:11:27.250
Giant gatekeepers?!

239
00:11:27.250 --> 00:11:28.790
That just isn't fair!

240
00:11:29.130 --> 00:11:33.010
They're huge! They make our
Mighty Destroyers look tiny.

241
00:11:34.510 --> 00:11:36.470
Now, turn back!

242
00:11:36.470 --> 00:11:38.050
I won't let you through this gate!

243
00:11:38.050 --> 00:11:40.050
Neither will Oimo!

244
00:11:40.050 --> 00:11:41.350
Here they come!

245
00:11:41.350 --> 00:11:45.640
No matter our foe, stand tall, Franky Family!

246
00:11:46.060 --> 00:11:47.270
This is for Bro!

247
00:11:47.270 --> 00:11:51.110
– Yeah!
– Yeah!

248
00:11:52.570 --> 00:11:55.320
Hey, you get it, right?

249
00:11:55.820 --> 00:11:56.950
Yeah.

250
00:11:56.950 --> 00:11:58.910
All right!

251
00:12:01.120 --> 00:12:05.500
If not us, then who could possibly face 'em?!

252
00:12:05.500 --> 00:12:10.920
Dismantling ships has made us
powerful enough to match these giants any day!

253
00:12:10.920 --> 00:12:12.420
Destroyers!

254
00:12:35.530 --> 00:12:39.070
O-Our Mighty Destroyers were...!

255
00:12:39.070 --> 00:12:41.030
It happened so fast!

256
00:12:42.870 --> 00:12:46.040
We were born warriors!

257
00:12:46.040 --> 00:12:51.670
The blood in our veins is different
from that of overgrown humans.

258
00:12:52.710 --> 00:12:55.630
I'm not gonna let even a single person pass!

259
00:12:55.630 --> 00:12:56.760
Neither will Oimo!

260
00:12:56.760 --> 00:12:59.510
D-D-Don't get cold feet!

261
00:12:59.510 --> 00:13:01.510
Don't give up!

262
00:13:01.510 --> 00:13:05.600
That's right! Big Bro Franky is
on the other side of that gate!

263
00:13:07.220 --> 00:13:12.060
Show them a fight worthy of
Bro's name, Franky Family!

264
00:13:20.820 --> 00:13:22.780
Hey, Straw Hat Luffy.

265
00:13:23.240 --> 00:13:25.990
How many friends did you bring?

266
00:13:27.620 --> 00:13:30.710
There are 10,000 soldiers on Enies Lobby!

267
00:13:31.540 --> 00:13:33.920
Yeah, I'm by myself.

268
00:13:37.170 --> 00:13:38.880
And you're in my way!

269
00:13:46.310 --> 00:13:50.680
Show them a fight worthy of
Bro's name, Franky Family!

270
00:13:56.480 --> 00:13:58.280
Don't give up!

271
00:13:58.280 --> 00:14:00.820
Open the path for Rocketman!

272
00:14:06.830 --> 00:14:09.330
Break open the gate!

273
00:14:13.080 --> 00:14:16.540
We're not gonna let
even an ant pass through this gate!

274
00:14:23.010 --> 00:14:24.260
Destroyers!

275
00:14:24.260 --> 00:14:25.300
Everyone!

276
00:14:26.600 --> 00:14:30.470
Dammit! You've already beaten
some of our strongest men?!

277
00:14:30.470 --> 00:14:32.100
Go!

278
00:14:40.150 --> 00:14:41.440
What the...?!

279
00:14:41.900 --> 00:14:43.070
Zambai!

280
00:14:43.070 --> 00:14:44.030
Kiwi! Mozu!

281
00:14:44.360 --> 00:14:45.860
Galley-La!

282
00:14:50.370 --> 00:14:51.910
Sorry we're late!

283
00:14:51.910 --> 00:14:55.500
Switching Sodom and Gomorrah
to land mode took longer than expected!

284
00:14:56.000 --> 00:14:58.920
Zambai! The Destroyers...!

285
00:14:58.920 --> 00:15:00.590
I know.

286
00:15:01.340 --> 00:15:04.220
But we can't stop to patch them up just yet.

287
00:15:04.220 --> 00:15:10.890
In order to get to where Bro is,
we have to open this gate at any cost!

288
00:15:11.310 --> 00:15:12.310
Let's go!

289
00:15:12.930 --> 00:15:13.520
Yeah!

290
00:15:15.850 --> 00:15:18.860
Let's throw him off balance, Mozu!

291
00:15:18.860 --> 00:15:21.110
Roger, Kiwi!

292
00:15:28.740 --> 00:15:31.080
– Hull Dismantler Slash!
– Hull Dismantler Slash!

293
00:15:34.330 --> 00:15:36.000
Rope Action...

294
00:15:36.460 --> 00:15:39.170
Timber Hitch Tug!

295
00:15:41.000 --> 00:15:44.970
Ow, ow, ow, ow!

296
00:15:52.010 --> 00:15:53.390
Kashi!

297
00:15:58.940 --> 00:15:59.860
Tilestone!

298
00:15:59.860 --> 00:16:01.400
Yeah!

299
00:16:11.660 --> 00:16:14.540
Ow, ow, ow, ow...!

300
00:16:14.540 --> 00:16:16.040
Trunnel Lock!

301
00:16:16.040 --> 00:16:17.620
A job well done!

302
00:16:29.590 --> 00:16:31.930
You rats!

303
00:16:31.930 --> 00:16:34.220
I'm gonna crush you!

304
00:16:40.730 --> 00:16:42.190
Kashi!

305
00:16:49.240 --> 00:16:50.610
All right!

306
00:16:55.200 --> 00:16:56.750
How dare you...!

307
00:16:57.450 --> 00:17:00.080
Just one more to go, gang!

308
00:17:00.080 --> 00:17:02.460
– Yeah!
– Yeah!

309
00:17:09.340 --> 00:17:10.970
So, what's the current situation?

310
00:17:10.970 --> 00:17:16.810
Sir, Kashi and Oimo are dealing with them
right now, in front of the island gate.

311
00:17:16.810 --> 00:17:18.600
We don't foresee any issues.

312
00:17:18.600 --> 00:17:19.810
I see.

313
00:17:19.810 --> 00:17:22.980
Then, you captured Straw Hat,
the main island's infiltrator?

314
00:17:22.980 --> 00:17:25.480
Well... uh...

315
00:17:25.480 --> 00:17:29.320
this is just an estimate,
but there are about 400...

316
00:17:29.860 --> 00:17:30.900
Four hundred?

317
00:17:31.530 --> 00:17:33.030
What are you talking about?

318
00:17:33.030 --> 00:17:34.870
Our casualties, sir!

319
00:17:41.960 --> 00:17:44.250
Huh?! Our casualties?!

320
00:17:44.250 --> 00:17:46.750
Are you saying that 400 guards are down?!

321
00:17:47.250 --> 00:17:49.840
You can probably add a hundred more...

322
00:17:50.470 --> 00:17:52.840
Uh, apologies. I need to revise that estimate.

323
00:17:52.840 --> 00:17:56.220
One would hope!
Our guards aren't exactly trash.

324
00:17:56.220 --> 00:17:58.270
There's no way it's that many!

325
00:17:58.270 --> 00:18:01.180
If there are casualties,
report them accurately!

326
00:18:08.150 --> 00:18:10.530
Um... Very well. Here is the report.

327
00:18:10.530 --> 00:18:12.400
As of now, the casualty count is five–

328
00:18:13.530 --> 00:18:15.700
Gah...!

329
00:18:16.580 --> 00:18:18.330
Five guards?!

330
00:18:18.330 --> 00:18:20.540
So it was actually just five guards?!

331
00:18:20.540 --> 00:18:23.790
Come on! You can't even
make a proper report!

332
00:18:23.790 --> 00:18:27.040
Five... hundred... gu...

333
00:18:28.550 --> 00:18:33.510
Rather than fighting, Straw Hat Luffy
is just running around the island.

334
00:18:33.510 --> 00:18:35.260
Well, that's just natural.

335
00:18:35.260 --> 00:18:38.310
No one is stupid enough
to fight that many guards.

336
00:18:38.310 --> 00:18:42.060
It's just a matter of time before he's captured.

337
00:18:44.440 --> 00:18:45.980
Welcome back, sirs and madam.

338
00:18:46.650 --> 00:18:49.730
Chief, Mr. Lucci's party has arrived.

339
00:18:50.190 --> 00:18:52.190
They're back?

340
00:18:52.190 --> 00:18:53.400
Let them in!

341
00:18:55.990 --> 00:18:58.200
Hey, Sogeking...

342
00:18:59.790 --> 00:19:00.370
Hey!

343
00:19:00.370 --> 00:19:02.790
Hey, that hurt!

344
00:19:02.790 --> 00:19:06.040
How do I use this cold air baton?

345
00:19:06.040 --> 00:19:08.000
Huh? Let me see...

346
00:19:08.000 --> 00:19:09.800
I wouldn't know!

347
00:19:12.340 --> 00:19:14.720
Now, guys! It's time!

348
00:19:16.260 --> 00:19:18.140
Let's go, shall we?

349
00:19:18.510 --> 00:19:21.520
They should've opened
those two gates by now.

350
00:19:21.520 --> 00:19:24.980
Charge ahead! Charge ahead!

351
00:19:25.770 --> 00:19:29.360
Samurai man! Take care of the iron fence!

352
00:19:29.980 --> 00:19:31.690
Leave it to me.

353
00:19:47.550 --> 00:19:54.090
I know there’s something that I need to say,

354
00:19:54.470 --> 00:19:58.060
but I can’t seem to find the words

355
00:19:58.310 --> 00:20:05.940
Wandering aimlessly, forever on the hunt, that’s how I’ve lived

356
00:20:05.940 --> 00:20:11.700
And now there’s something right in front of me,

357
00:20:12.900 --> 00:20:16.410
a light that shines brighter than gold

358
00:20:16.780 --> 00:20:21.790
But as I trail behind, it speeds out of sight.

359
00:20:21.790 --> 00:20:28.380
What’s going on? Scared of what’s yet to come

360
00:20:28.710 --> 00:20:34.630
So many times, so many times as we both stumbled on the way

361
00:20:34.840 --> 00:20:37.640
We’ve had our highs, we’ve had our lows;

362
00:20:37.930 --> 00:20:40.720
Yeah, we just take it day by day

363
00:20:41.020 --> 00:20:47.270
Never forget that even when the night snuffs out the light

364
00:20:47.560 --> 00:20:53.900
When the dark has passed the sun will rise again
